piled .bpf.o files and reports minimum kernel version, helpers, maps, and portability issues","url":"https://github.com/boratanrikulu/bpfvet","score":4,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"\u003cp\u003eBuilt this to answer \"what's the oldest kernel this BPF program can run on?\" without reading changelogs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFeed it any .bpf.o file and it tells you:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMinimum kernel version (computed from helpers, prog types, map types)b\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTransport mechanism (RingBuf, PerfEventArray, maps)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCO-RE coverage and BTF presence\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuperseded helper usage (bpf_probe_read -\u0026gt; bpf_probe_read_kernel)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWorks on compiled ELF, not source-language agnostic.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"Built this to answer \"what's the oldest kernel this BPF program can run on?\" without reading changelogs.\r\n\r\nFeed it any .bpf.o file and it tells you:  \r\n- Minimum kernel version (computed from helpers, prog types, map types)b \r\n- Transport mechanism (RingBuf, PerfEventArray, maps)  \r\n- CO-RE coverage and BTF presence   \r\n- Superseded helper usage (bpf_probe_read -\u003e bpf_probe_read_kernel)\r\n\r\nWorks on compiled ELF, not source-language agnostic.","submitter_user":"boratanrikulu","user_is_author":true,"tags":["linux","networking"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/30vbek","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/30vbek/bpfvet_analyzes_compiled_bpf_o_files"},{"short_id":"y5nowq","created_at":"2026-04-20T04:07:49.000-05:00","title":"Modern Frontend Complexity: essential or accidental?","url":"https://binaryigor.com/modern-frontend-complexity.html","score":16,"flags":1,"comment_count":31,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"BinaryIgor","user_is_author":true,"tags":["web"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/y5nowq","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/y5nowq/modern_frontend_complexity_essential"},{"short_id":"1akblt","created_at":"2026-04-20T03:17:56.000-05:00","title":"Obelisk 0.37: JavaScript, Deployments, Cron","url":"https://obeli.sk/blog/announcing-obelisk-0-37/","score":6,"flags":0,"comment_count":1,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"tomas","user_is_author":true,"tags":["release","rust","wasm"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/1akblt","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/1akblt/obelisk_0_37_javascript_deployments_cron"}]